$interpreted: Dagger: So, allies indeed?
Kittyeyes: You troll, how could you!
Nolva: Hold up. Kittyeyes, Roger's...
Roger: ……….
Dagger: Hmph. Still standing strong? Then I'll——
Kittyeyes: OH NO!
Dagger: Holy toledo! What you are you guys doing here?
Kittyeyes: You're the cause of brother's madness! You must help me pin him down!
Nolva: Um, Roger's quite a sight in beast mode......
Dagger: And your point is?
Nolva: If we don't give it everything we've got, we're screwed.
Kittyeyes: If you hurt more than brother's feelings, I'll see to it that you get what's coming!
Dagger: What have I gotten myself into...
Dagger: Whatever, I don't need help. I can defeat him alone!
Roger: URGHHHHH!!!!
Kittyeyes: And you were saying?
Nolva: Don't push it.
Dagger: Hmph!
Roger: AAARRRGGGGHHH!!!!!
Kittyeyes: Sis Nolva, how's he doing?
Nolva: Got him under control for now...
Nolva: The void seasons are totally out of wack and it's affecting Roger.
Dagger: Hey, what's going on?
Kittyeyes: It's going down! Why'd you attack brother?
Dagger: Aren't you... the ones that kidnapped the princess?
Kittyeyes: What princess? Never in my life have I even seen one!
Dagger: But the rune chariot that kidnapped the princess is here?
Nolva: Roger spotted a group of strange people abandoning the cart here last night.
Nolva: He came over this morning to check it out.
Dagger: Is that so...? Let me check it out.
Dagger: Damn! An empty shell, just like the one the princess was in. Nothing is inside.
Dagger: Went through all that to prepare a dummy wagon? Have I been wasting my time?
Kittyeyes: That's none of our business! But injuring brother for no good reason, don't you owe him an apology?
Dagger: ...My apologies...is he alright?

Nolva: Flesh wounds will heal. But engaging in combat
triggered the side effects of his void disease.
Nolva: Once he awakens, he will still be raging.
Dagger: Void disease?
Kittyeyes: All we can do is ask him to treat brother's sickness.
Nolva: Dr. Clovis will not pity you. Perhaps I should come along?
Kittyeyes: Tall guy, what's your name?
Dagger: Me? You can call me Dagger.
Kittyeyes: I'm Kittyeyes, and big sis here is Nolva. The injured guy is my brother Roger.
Kittyeyes: Please take brother with us to go see the doctor.
Dagger: What? But I have a mission to tend——
Kittyeyes: ——if you didn't hit him first, would he be like this?
Nolva: And if Roger turns, we'll need you to help sedate him again...
Dagger: Why me? Alright alright. I was wrong, I will take responsibility.
Dagger: Which way are we heading?
Kittyeyes: Come with us, it'll take half a day's journey.
